# The issuer-service Docker image bakes in Sunspot circuit artefacts from
# circuits/target/zksettle_slice.{json,ccs,pk}. Keep that subtree shipped to
# Railway; the rest of circuits/ (Noir source, intermediates) is not needed
# at runtime. **/target/ above already excludes circuits/target by default,
# so we re-include the dir then whitelist the 3 artefacts the runtime reads.
!circuits/target/
circuits/target/*
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.json
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.ccs
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.pk
